:attr:`~icalendar.prop.binary.vBinary.obj` is deprecated in favor of :attr:`~icalendar.prop.binary.vBinary.bytes`. It is retained as a lossy string view of the value for backward compatibility, and will be removed in icalendar 8. The ``test_ical_value_rejects_non_base64_characters`` test was removed because :attr:`vBinary.ical_value <icalendar.prop.binary.vBinary.ical_value>` no longer validates or decodes Base64. @uwezkhan
